{"tid":2430631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「道德撚勿入」「上車機會」係時候推晒D廢老打科興，中獎死左可以拿300萬","createTime":"2021-03-03T05:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T00:01:36.000Z","uid":43785,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3986206869d90f67177a0c91e04879826b239a","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"市民續接種科興：生死有命唔使驚　長期病患市民：要問過醫生 繼續有市民到場接種科興疫苗。有長者認為死亡事件是「萬分之一」，加上未證實與疫苗有關，他亦無長期病患，感到放心。有長者就認為「生死有命」，認為國產疫苗始終最適合中國人，「唔使驚」。有血壓高和心臟病的長者，就指本身想接種疫苗，但現時要先問過醫生。<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">有年輕人陪同婆婆到場接種</span></span>，指有長期病患的父親，本身打算稍後接種科興疫苗，但現時會「睇定啲」，或會接種另一種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381340&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e0dc1dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381340</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完紅字明白左D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老人家與奇擺係度等死，不如送佢去打大陸針搏一搏，隨時脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜事都冇又可以做孝子，幫親人防疫（雖然成效極低）。<br />\n成件事一舉兩得，老人家死左又可以益後人發達。好過留係度獻世。<br />\n<br />\n後生仔有錢就可以了做自己喜歡做既事，移民又好做乜都好。幫自己夢想成真，努力少幾十年。<br />\n<br />\n係，道德撚可能睇完覺得搏賠償好仆街，但呢個世界賺錢既，有邊個唔仆街？<br />\n有能力既人咪又係踐踏其他平民既屍骸向上爬。<br />\n<br />\n去下打針現場啦。呢個就係真正既社會。道德規限從來都只係政府用來維穩用既工具來炸。<br />\n<br />\n用科興針，殺一個廢老藍絲，幫自己賺幾百萬，何樂而不為。<br />\n我驚有人睇完呢單野，怕政府唔再用科興，拿拿臨趕住推撚埋老豆老母去打TIM呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301bb5843f475b753926d46d90cb2a3be058bbbb","tid":2430631,"uid":340189,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:24:01.000Z","msg":"你點害香港人的？"},{"pid":"8084e9bba47abc8810b116eb3d8fe0be4e3bd2ec","tid":2430631,"uid":246156,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"你點推的"},{"pid":"7791ed248a6c2407b33d8ac8ee696f0ac2ad914a","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"全民推廢老打科興大行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646db67aff57a9b20d8e89e3a74ea32c90442a38","tid":2430631,"uid":340189,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"你點殺的？"},{"pid":"1f2b2b1d2532d3e249a06e5b9e543372ca152aff","tid":2430631,"uid":247020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"可憐天下父母心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd303a79ff4a7462df31ec3a8cb58f12a7ffe4b","tid":2430631,"uid":261505,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir !<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WVRM4c.png&h=ec331784&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUnkBNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUnkBNd.png&h=90cb38b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OxTuVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OxTuVp.jpg&h=2a6085f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPJaEwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPJaEwL.png&h=08788276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAOgdKf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAOgdKf.png&h=f53d1a95&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzHj9Wq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzHj9Wq.png&h=47ee8948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixiOV3r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi