s://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAezwn0.png&h=0bd2c168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b46RyBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb46RyBk.png&h=2e2fbec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來大陸60歲以上冇得打<br />\n香港老野做白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢鋪正，真係可以推老人家去搏賺賠償了"},{"pid":"7629aa2446f6eb97f8ed02778273beccfb74b31b","tid":2430631,"uid":217861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076a17656f154b49312e9f639a656ae87587b2d4","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7997b4b8ce6b1e31737d198e0a7237ef460d08b4","tid":2430631,"uid":305269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"爺爺，你之前咪話想幫我供樓嘅？你要身體健康先得㗎，不如我陪你去打疫苗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,你點知的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"冇事就做孝子，出事都係做孝子<br />\n<br />\n孝子，你今日做左未？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲叫環保上車法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da99ee7b33233c91918035440b2e68bdb3e83254","tid":2430631,"uid":70781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea3986206869d90f67177a0c91e04879826b239a","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"市民續接種科興：生死有命唔使驚　長期病患市民：要問過醫生 繼續有市民到場接種科興疫苗。有長者認為死亡事件是「萬分之一」，加上未證實與疫苗有關，他亦無長期病患，感到放心。有長者就認為「生死有命」，認為國產疫苗始終最適合中國人，「唔使驚」。有血壓高和心臟病的長者，就指本身想接種疫苗，但現時要先問過醫生。<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">有年輕人陪同婆婆到場接種</span></span>，指有長期病患的父親，本身打算稍後接種科興疫苗，但現時會「睇定啲」，或會接種另一種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381340&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e0dc1dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381340</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完紅字明白左D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老人家與奇擺係度等死，不如送佢去打大陸針搏一搏，隨時脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜事都冇又可以做孝子，幫親人防疫（雖然成效極低）。<br />\n成件事一舉兩得，老人家死左又可以益後人發達。好過留係度獻世。<br />\n<br />\n後生仔有錢就可以了做自己喜歡做既事，移民又好做乜都好。幫自己夢想成真，努力少幾十年。<br />\n<br />\n係，道德撚可能睇完覺得搏賠償好仆街，但呢個世界賺錢既，有邊個唔仆街？<br />\n有能力既人咪又係踐踏其他平民既屍骸向上爬。<br />\n<br />\n去下打針現場啦。呢個就係真正既社會。道德規限從來都只係政府用來維穩用既工具來炸。<br />\n<br />\n用科興針，殺一個廢老藍絲，幫自己賺幾百萬，何樂而不為。<br />\n我驚有人睇完呢單野，怕政府唔再用科興，拿拿臨趕住推撚埋老豆老母去打TIM呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7XdMYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7XdMYA.jpg&h=36c202c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n領嘢瓜撚埋都未必有得攞㗎"},{"pid":"2cf804ae6ab48f5a965657d4ca1e5ec4015c711b","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7629aa2446f6eb97f8ed02778273beccfb74b31b","tid":2430631,"uid":217861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"076a17656f154b49312e9f639a656ae87587b2d4","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7997b4b8ce6b1e31737d198e0a7237ef460d08b4","tid":2430631,"uid":305269,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"爺爺，你之前咪話想幫我供樓嘅？你要身體健康先得㗎，不如我陪你去打疫苗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,你點知的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"冇事就做孝子，出事都係做孝子<br />\n<br />\n孝子，你今日做左未？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:03:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲叫環保上車法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"為上車可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23727b718e03ad881c05f161280392e45b79d7d4","tid":2430631,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc